        {
            "title": "美股日誌｜ 打定唔打？　輸得起先好買！",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"美股日誌｜ 打定唔打？ 輸得起先好買！\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/x2Bu3OQ7ZoQZb.2eJyj2OQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/6d16d2e0-27cc-11f1-a7c5-d5ada77bfe19\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美股日誌｜ 打定唔打？ 輸得起先好買！</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗局勢一日都嫌長，今日話打，明天又改口，跟車太貼隨時被人左一巴、右一巴。想贏錢的話，最好要有心理準備輸得起。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國股市周二變動偏軟，特朗普表示美國正與伊朗進行談判，同時有報道指五角大樓計劃向中東派遣精銳部隊，以恢復霍爾木茲海峽通航，實在令人精神。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">道指下跌0.2%；標普500指數下跌0.4%；以科技股為主的納斯達克綜合指數下跌 0.8%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"1\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"下載Yahoo財經APP\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:下載Yahoo財經APP;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://mobile.yahoo.com/finance?pid=editorial&amp;c=HK_Acquisition_YMktg_Evergreen_article_&amp;af_sub1=Acquisition&amp;af_sub2=HK_YMktg&amp;af_sub4=1058&amp;af_sub5=article__Banner_&amp;uuid=eDFkEhESdIhPGYRE2850\"><ins>下載Yahoo財經APP</ins></a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美股外幣即時報價 多國新聞任睇<br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3月24日（星期二）市况</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b9a590fc-4858-45b5-8851-2eed6127022d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"2\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"道瓊斯指數\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:道瓊斯指數;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EDJI\"><ins> 道瓊斯指數</ins></a> 跌84.75點或0.18%，報46,123.72點。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"3\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"標普500指數\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:標普500指數;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EGSPC\"><ins> 標普500指數</ins></a> 跌24.64點或0.37%，報6,556.38點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:4;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"4\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"納斯達克指數\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:納斯達克指數;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EIXIC\"><ins> 納斯達克指數</ins></a> 跌184.87點或0.84%，報21,761.89點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:5;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"5\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"紐約5月期油\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:紐約5月期油;cpos:5;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/CL=F\"><ins> 紐約5月期油</ins></a> 收報88.39美元一桶，跌3.96美元或4.29%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:6;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"6\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"紐約4月期金\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:紐約4月期金;cpos:6;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/GC=F\"><ins> 紐約4月期金</ins></a> 收報4,474.9美元一盎司，升67.6美元或1.53%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:7;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"7\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"比特幣\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:比特幣;cpos:7;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/BTC-USD/\"><ins> 比特幣</ins></a> 截至美東時間下午4時報69,276.39美元，跌1,403.03美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:8;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"8\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"美國10年期國債息率\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:美國10年期國債息率;cpos:8;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5ETNX\"><ins> 美國10年期國債息率</ins></a> 收報4.392厘。<br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">另一方面，特朗普周二下午在白宮向記者表示，美國正與伊朗「合適的人」進行接觸，並稱「他們非常希望達成協議」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他的言論呼應周一對談判「具建設性」的描述。油價周一因市場憧憬戰事降溫而急跌，但隨着伊朗與美國及以色列聯盟之間的戰鬥持續，油價其後回升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國3月企業活動成長放緩至近一年來最低水平，材料及其他投入品的支付價格在伊朗戰爭爆發後上升。本周二公佈的數據，標普全球3月綜合產出指數初值下降0.5點至51.4。讀數高於50表示擴張。支付價格指標上升逾3點，至5月以來最高水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">整體綜合指標回落，主要由於服務業活動成長降至近一年來最弱水平。服務業投入價格升至5月以來最高，而製造業投入成本升至七個月高位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">標普全球市場財智首席商業經濟學家Chris Williamson表示：「企業表示，衝突帶來的額外不確定性，以及對生活成本的影響，導致需求受衝擊。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">個股方面，晶片設計公司<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:9;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"9\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Arm\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Arm;cpos:9;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/ARM/\">Arm</a>(ARM.US)周二宣佈新AI數據中心晶片AGI CPU，計劃在今年下半年投入量產，料將帶來數十億美元的收入。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:10;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"10\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Meta\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Meta;cpos:10;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/META/\">Meta</a>(META.US)將成為該公司AGI CPU的主要合作夥伴，兩家公司曾共同參與設計。Arm的新晶片客戶包括OpenAI、Cloudflare(NET.US)、SAP和SK Telecom。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">軟件股受壓，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:11;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"11\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Salesforce(\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Salesforce(;cpos:11;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/CRM/\">Salesforce(</a>CRM.US)跌超6%。科技股多數下跌，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:12;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"12\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"微軟\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:微軟;cpos:12;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/MSFT/\">微軟</a>(MSFT.US)租用OpenAI及<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:13;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"13\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"甲骨文\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:甲骨文;cpos:13;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/ORCL/\">甲骨文</a>(ORCL.US)棄租德州數據中心，微軟跌超過2%。亞馬遜(AMZN.US)巴林服務再因伊朗戰火中斷，跌1.4%。 據報日本第二大銀行三井住友金融集團計劃收購<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:14;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"14\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"富瑞\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:富瑞;cpos:14;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/JEF/\">富瑞</a>(JEF.US)，富瑞股價逆市升2.5%。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E6%97%A5%E8%AA%8C%EF%BD%9C-%E6%89%93%E5%AE%9A%E5%94%94%E6%89%93%EF%BC%9F-%E8%BC%B8%E5%BE%97%E8%B5%B7%E5%85%88%E5%A5%BD%E8%B2%B7%EF%BC%81-220234163.html",
